.DT
notify_npc_event
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
notify_npc_event

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
notify_npc_event -  This method is called when an event needs to be notified about.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs void notify_npc_event(string event,
mixed * information ...)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^event%^RESET%^ - the event to tell us about
%^BOLD%^information%^RESET%^ - the information associated with the event

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/npc/goals_inherit.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method is called when an event needs to be notified about.
The event handling routines should try to be short.  They should
just modify the priority of something, or add a new goal to the
current list.
.EP

